 “Palworld”否认游戏奖冷落：“并非一切都是阴谋” https://www.nme.com/news/gaming-news/palworld-denies-game-awards-snub-conspiracy-nintendo-legal-3815566?utm_source=rss&utm_medium=rss&utm_campaign=palworld-denies-game-awards-snub-阴谋任天堂法律Ali ShutlerMon, 25 Nov 2024 11:59:53 +0000 Gaming NewsNews https://www.nme.com/?p=3815566 <p><img width="2000" height="1270" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/Palworld-2024-screenshot.jpg" class="attachment-full size-full wp-post-image" alt="友世界" decoding="async" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/Palworld-2024-screenshot.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/Palworld-2024-screenshot-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/Palworld-2024-screenshot-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/Palworld-2024-screenshot-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/Palworld-2024-screenshot-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/Palworld-2024-screenshot-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p>一些粉丝认为零提名是由于与任天堂正在进行的法律斗争</p><p><a href="https://www.nme.com/news/gaming-news/palworld-denies-game-awards-snub-conspiracy-nintendo-legal-3815566">《Palworld》否认游戏奖冷落：“并非一切都是阴谋”的</a>帖子首先出现在<a href="https://www.nme.com">NME</a>上。</p> ; <p><img width="2000" height="1270" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/Palworld-2024-screenshot.jpg" class="attachment-full size-full wp-post-image" alt="友世界" decoding="async" loading="lazy" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/Palworld-2024-screenshot.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/Palworld-2024-screenshot-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/Palworld-2024-screenshot-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/Palworld-2024-screenshot-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/Palworld-2024-screenshot-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/Palworld-2024-screenshot-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p> 2024 年游戏奖提名名单已于上周公布，而<em><a href="https://www.nme.com/games/palworld">Palworld</a></em>并未在 30 个类别中的任何一个类别中被提及。</p><ul><li><strong>了解更多： <a href="https://www.nme.com/features/palworld-a-tale-of-adorable-monsters-friends-late-stage-capitalism-labour-exploitation-2985030">Pocketpair Inc 的首席执行官：“我们不希望‘Palworld’变得美丽和完美。我们希望注入更黑暗主题的元素，包括剥削和暴力”</a></strong></li></ul><p> 2024 年游戏大奖将于 12 月 13 日举行，旨在表彰视频游戏行业的成就。 <em><a href="https://www.nme.com/games/astro-bot">《Astro Bot》</a></em>和<em><a href="https://www.nme.com/games/final-fantasy-vii-rebirth">《最终幻想 7：重生》</a></em> <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/gaming-news/astro-bot-and-final-fantasy-7-rebirth-lead-2024-game-award-nominations-3813944">分别获得七项提名，领跑今年的竞赛</a>，而<em>《Balatro》、</em> <em><a href="https://www.nme.com/games/black-myth-wukong">《黑神话：悟空》</a> 、 <a href="https://www.nme.com/features/gaming-features/elden-ring-shadow-of-the-erdtree-expansion-dlc-3766304">《埃尔登指环：树影之影》</a></em>和<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/gaming-news/metaphor-refantazio-is-one-of-the-best-reviewed-games-of-2024-3800630"><em>《隐喻：ReFantazio》</em></a>也入围了年度游戏奖。</p><p>尽管<em>《Palworld》</em>是 2024 年最受关注和最成功的游戏之一，但这款开放世界生存游戏并未在今年的颁奖典礼上获得任何奖项。而且，粉丝们对这种冷落并不满意。一位玩家<a href="https://x.com/AzuriCAW/status/1858653013608722894" target="_blank" rel="noopener">写道</a>：“在游戏颁奖典礼上没有提及<em>Palworld</em>是疯狂的。”另一位玩家<a href="https://x.com/llouck7/status/1860111772730159356" target="_blank" rel="noopener">则称</a>其为“疯狂”。</p><p>另一位粉丝<a href="https://x.com/MagykRose/status/1858919281012207803" target="_blank" rel="noopener">表示</a>：“我认为<em>Palworld</em>永远无法进入今年游戏奖提名的原因是他们与任天堂之间的法律纠纷。”九月，任天堂和神奇宝贝公司发表了<a href="https://www.nintendo.co.jp/corporate/release/en/2024/240919.html">一份联合声明</a>，确认<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/gaming-news/pokemon-is-suing-palworld-for-copyright-infringement-3795078">他们已就侵犯版权向 Palworld 开发商 Pocketpair 提起诉讼</a>。</p><blockquote class="twitter-tweet" data-width="550" data-dnt="true"><p lang="en" dir="ltr">我认为 Palworld 永远不会进入今年游戏奖提名的原因是他们与任天堂之间的法律纠纷。</p><p>这对任天堂来说是一个真正的耻辱，并且欺负小公司。</p><p> — 𝓜𝓮𝓻𝓻𝔂𝓶𝓪𝓴𝓮𝓻𝓜𝓪𝓰𝔂𝓴𝓡𝓸𝓼𝓮 <img src="https://s.w.org/images/core/emoji/15.0.3/72x72/1f51e.png" alt="🔞" class="wp-smiley" style="height: 1em; max-height: 1em;" /> ENVtuber (@MagykRose) <a href="https://twitter.com/MagykRose/status/1858919281012207803?ref_src=twsrc%5Etfw">2024 年 11 月 19 日</a></p></blockquote><p><script async src="https://platform.twitter.com/widgets.js" charset="utf-8"></script></p><p> Pocketpair 称这起诉讼“ <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/gaming-news/palworld-responds-to-truly-unfortunate-nintendo-lawsuit-3795221">确实很不幸</a>”，并于本月早些时候声称<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/gaming-news/nintendo-wants-palworld-shut-down-copyright-infringement-legal-battle-3811574">任天堂希望关闭<em>Palworld，</em></a>直到法律纠纷得到解决。</p><p>针对缺乏游戏奖提名者， <em>Palworld</em>全球社区经理 Bucky<a href="https://x.com/Bucky_cm/status/1858578343941337286" target="_blank" rel="noopener">写道</a>：“不，我不认为 Palworld 受到冷落。推特已经变成了一个毫无幽默感的地方。别再成为戏剧性的游戏玩家了。并非一切都是阴谋。”</p><p>其他人则认为，由于<em>Palworld</em>仍处于抢先体验阶段，因此它无论如何都没有资格获得 2024 年奖项。然而，巴基<a href="https://x.com/Bucky_cm/status/1858622325769597063" target="_blank" rel="noopener">确实指出</a>，抢先体验版<em>《庄园领主》</em>已获得两个不同类别的提名。</p><p>尽管与任天堂的法律斗争仍在继续， <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/gaming-news/you-can-now-play-palworld-on-playstation-despite-nintendo-legal-issues-3796930"><em>Palworld</em>最近在 PlayStation 上推出</a>，并<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/gaming-news/palworld-is-set-to-come-to-mobile-3799647">确认了移动版本的计划</a>。</p><p>在其他新闻中，据报道<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/gaming-news/playstation-working-handheld-console-nintendo-switch-rival-3815549">PlayStation 正在开发一款手持游戏机来与 Nintendo Switch 竞争</a>。本月早些时候，Xbox 证实它<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/gaming-news/xbox-is-working-on-a-handheld-console-to-rival-the-nintendo-switch-3812753">也在明年 Switch 2 发布之前开发一款便携式游戏机</a>。</p><p> <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/gaming-news/palworld-denies-game-awards-snub-conspiracy-nintendo-legal-3815566">《Palworld》否认游戏奖冷落：“并非一切都是阴谋”的</a>帖子首先出现在<a href="https://www.nme.com">NME</a>上。</p> ;
